===Transitive verb===
'''to carry'''  ([[carries]], [[carried]], [[carrying]])

#<!--VTrTransport--> to [[lift]] and bring to somewhere else; to [[transport]] by lifting
#<!--VTrStock--> to [[stock]] or [[supply]]
#:''The corner drugstore doesn't '''carry''' his favorite brand of aspirin.''
#<!--VTrTakeOver-->to [[adopt]]; [[take over]] or [[stand in]]
#:''I think I can carry Smith's work while she is out.''
#<!--VTrTransfer--> when [[adding]] numbers by hand, to move a quantity in excess of what is countable in the [[units]] in a column into the column with the next higher units
#:''Five and nine are fourteen; '''carry''' the one to the tens place.''
#To [[have]] or [[maintain]].
#:''Always '''carry''' sufficient insurance to protect against a loss.''

